cActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5829212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kko1705481411881.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kko1705481411881.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kko1705481411881.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"exx1665702675164\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                             \n Setup Utility\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Setup Utility enables users to change selected initialization settings in <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> without restarting the application. It can be added to the system menu of an MDI Uniface desktop application.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702675164__p_d12575e1_d12576e1_d12577e1\">To enable the Setup utility in your application, in the Properties Inspector of the application shell, click the ellipsis in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window/App</span> to open that properties dialog, then select <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Setup</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702675164__p_d12578e1_d12579e1_d12580e1\">To display the Setup utility in the application, click the icon in the application title bar to display the application menu, and then choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Setup</span>.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"exx1665702675164__fig_d12581e1_d12582e1_d12583e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Uniface Setup Utility</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Uniface Setup Utility\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/setuputility.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702675164__p_d12587e1_d12588e1_d12589e1\">Each tab contains a group of related properties, in most cases from the same file section.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Setup Utility Tabs</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n Tab\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n Setting\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n Initialization Setting\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n More Information\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     User \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">User</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Password</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">User</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Password</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypz1665702565044.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypz1665702565044.html\" title=\"Get or set the name of a Struct member, as it is known to its parent.\">$name</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lfx1718886557390.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lfx1718886557390.html\" title=\"Return the encrypted password used to log on to a database path.\">$password</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"3\">\n                     Colors \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Foreground</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Normal</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Bright</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Blink</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">BrightBlink</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lar1665702646046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lar1665702646046.html\" title=\"The [background] and [foreground] sections of the initialization file determine how Uniface video attributes are mapped to Uniface index colors for Windows and character mode applications.\">[background] and [foreground]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Bright</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Blink</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Bright</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Blink</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sza1665702675334.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sza1665702675334.html\" title=\"The [colors] section of the initialization file contains settings that determine whether bright and blink video attributes are set when using Uniface index colors.\">[colors]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Use Microsoft Windows color scheme for color NO</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Widget Color Zero equal to Color=No</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">SystemColors</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ColorZero</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"djh1665702617281.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/djh1665702617281.html\" title=\"Enables the use of default system colors as the foreground and background colors in forms.\">SystemColors</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vgt1665702615336.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vgt1665702615336.html\" title=\"Enables the use of default system colors as the foreground and background colors for objects on forms.\">ColorZero</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n                     Toolbar \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show Character Set</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show Font List</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show Style Buttons</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show View Buttons</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show Window List and Controls</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">CharSets</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">fontlist</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">StyleButtons</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ViewToggle</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">MdiControls</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qjq1665702674162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qjq1665702674162.html\" title=\"The [toolbar] section of the initialization file controls the content of the Uniface toolbar, which is available for all Uniface client/server applications. All settings in this section are automatically updated by Uniface whenever it terminates.\">[toolbar]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar and panel button style</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar and panel color</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ButtonStyle</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">PanelColor</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"avj1665702614940.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/avj1665702614940.html\" title=\"Specifies a style for the appearance of buttons and borders in the Uniface toolbar and panels.\">ButtonStyle</a>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fbn1665702616587.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbn1665702616587.html\" title=\"Determines the background color of panels.\">PanelColor</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     Fonts \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Screen Fonts</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Button Font</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Shift Font</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Printer Fonts</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Font0</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ButtonFont</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ShiftFont</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyv1665702675417.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyv1665702675417.html\" title=\"The [screen] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used in the GUI user interface and additional settings for screen display.\">[screen]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"4\">\n                     Miscellaneous \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Button Spacing</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Button Type</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Panel Type</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ButtonSpacing</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">ButtonType</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">PanelType</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abd1665702614863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abd1665702614863.html\" title=\"Determines the number of pixels between adjacent buttons on a panel.\">ButtonSpacing</a>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"byk1665702615020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byk1665702615020.html\" title=\"Specifies the type of button on session and component panels.\">ButtonType</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nlx1665702616810.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nlx1665702616810.html\" title=\"Enables or disables the session panel, and controls its position.\">PanelType</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Message</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transcript</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Debug</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">MsgLines</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">TransLines</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">DebugLinse</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gfw1665702616435.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gfw1665702616435.html\" title=\"The number of messages remembered by the message (status) line.\">MsgLines</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pah1665702617434.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pah1665702617434.html\" title=\"The number of lines remembered by the Transcript Window before it starts losing lines at the top.\">TransLines</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"orn1665702615412.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/orn1665702615412.html\" title=\"The number of lines remembered by the list box in the ProcScript Debugger.\">DebugLines</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Entity Frames</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Frames</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Focus Flash</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Line Spacing</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">FrameType</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">TextFrame</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">FocusFlash</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">LineSpace</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bcc1665702616083.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bcc1665702616083.html\" title=\"The type of graphic used to draw frames on components.\">FrameType</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fhw1665702617359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fhw1665702617359.html\" title=\"Set the type of border for editable Unifields.\">TextFrame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Sound Enabled</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">Sound</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vwu1665702617204.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vwu1665702617204.html\" title=\"Enables or disables all beeps and buzzes generated by Uniface.\">Sound</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     Advanced \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Minimum Resource Level</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Auto Maximize</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Async GUI</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">MinResource</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">AutoMaximize</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">AsyncGui</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tca1665702616360.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tca1665702616360.html\" title=\"The percentage of system resources that Uniface should try to leave available to other applications.\">MinResource</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vwy1665702614709.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vwy1665702614709.html\" title=\"Controls whether forms are automatically maximized when they do not fit in the application window. This setting also controls whether a component that was previously maximized is maximized again when it is run again.\">AutoMaximize</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vbk1665702614434.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vbk1665702614434.html\" title=\"Improve form appearance for applications using widgets with large ValRep lists.\">AsynchGui</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     Printer \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Printers</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Print Preview</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Print transparent background when Color set to No</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">LogPrinter</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">PreviewZoom</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ColorNo</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vas1665702670549.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vas1665702670549.html\" title=\"The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions.\">[printer]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     State \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete current layout geometry…</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Keep form layout geometry</span>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Include layout geometry for tab forms</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n Not stored\n <p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">History</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">SaveTabForm</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lwt1665702643471.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lwt1665702643471.html\" title=\"Number of lines kept in the widget, expressed as an integer from 1 through 10000. Default is 1000.\">History Size</a>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gqy1665702673733.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqy1665702673733.html\" title=\"Determines whether the layout of contained forms is saved from one session to the next.\">SaveContainedForm</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__1\">\n                     Editor \n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Color</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Size</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__3\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Code elements</var>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword option\">TabSize</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exx1665702675164__table_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ivc1665702674015.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ivc1665702674015.html\" title=\"The [procbox] section of the initialization file enables you to configure colors in the ProcScript Editor and HTML Source editor.\">[procbox]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5829212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5829212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Setup Utility Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Setup Utility The Setup Utility enables users to change selected initialization settings in usys.ini without restarting the application. It can be added to the system menu of an MDI Uniface desktop application. To enable the Setup utility in your application, in the Properties Inspector of the application shell, click the ellipsis in the Window/App to open that properties dialog, then select Setup . To display the Setup utility in the application, click the icon in the application title bar to display the application menu, and then choose Setup . Figure 1. Uniface Setup Utility Each tab contains a group of related properties, in most cases from the same file section. Table 1. Setup Utility Tabs Tab Setting Initialization Setting More Information User User Password User Password $name and $password Colors Foreground Background Normal Bright Blink BrightBlink [background] and [foreground] Bright Blink Bright Blink [colors] Use Microsoft Windows color scheme for color NO Widget Color Zero equal to Color=No SystemColors ColorZero SystemColors and ColorZero Toolbar Show Character Set Show Font List Show Style Buttons Show View Buttons Show Window List and Controls CharSets fontlist StyleButtons ViewToggle MdiControls [toolbar] Toolbar and panel button style Toolbar and panel color ButtonStyle PanelColor ButtonStyle PanelColor Fonts Screen Fonts Button Font Shift Font Printer Fonts Font0 ButtonFont ShiftFont [screen] Miscellaneous Button Spacing Button Type Panel Type ButtonSpacing ButtonType PanelType ButtonSpacing ButtonType PanelType Message Transcript Debug MsgLines TransLines DebugLinse MsgLines TransLines DebugLines Entity Frames Field Frames Focus Flash Line Spacing FrameType TextFrame FocusFlash LineSpace FrameType TextFrame Sound Enabled Sound Sound Advanced Minimum Resource Level Auto Maximize Async GUI MinResource AutoMaximize AsyncGui MinResource AutoMaximize AsynchGui Printer Printers Print Preview Print transparent background when Color set to No LogPrinter PreviewZoom ColorNo [printer] State Delete current layout geometry… Keep form layout geometry Include layout geometry for tab forms Not stored History SaveTabForm History Size SaveContainedForm Editor Color Tab Size Code elements TabSize [procbox] Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}